Package com.vector.cfg.model.groovy.api

Automation scripting API for convenient MDF model access in Groovy code clients.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IActiveEcuc
    IMdfModelNavigator
    IMdfReadApi
    The IMdfReadApi API provides methods which allow retrieving MDF model objects in different ways.
    IMdfReadCollectionConfigurator<T extends MIObject>
    The IMdfReadCollectionConfigurator provides means to configure the read navigator access (see IMdfModelNavigator for a collection of MDF objects.
    IMdfReadSingleConfigurator<T extends MIObject>
    The IMdfReadSingleConfigurator provides means to configure the read navigator access (see IMdfModelNavigator for a single MDF object.
    IMdfWriteApi
    The IMdfWriteApi API provides methods which allow modifying MDF model objects in different ways.
    IMdfWriteCollectionConfigurator<T extends MIObject>
    The IMdfWriteCollectionConfigurator provides means to configure the write navigator access (see IMdfModelNavigator for a collection of MDF objects.
    IMdfWriteListAddHasDefinitionExtensions<T extends com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIHasDefinition>
    The interface IMdfWriteListAddHasDefinitionExtensions defines some method extensions for MDF child lists to create and add new Ecuc object instances with definition (containers or parameters).
    IMdfWriteListAddReferrableExtensions<T extends com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.commoncore.autosar.MIReferrable>
    The interface IMdfWriteListAddReferrableExtensions defines some method extensions for MDF child lists to create and add new MIReferrable child objects.
    IMdfWriteListAddSubContainerExtensions
    The interface IMdfWriteListAddSubContainerExtensions defines some method extensions for MDF child lists to create and add new sub-containers.
    IMdfWriteListAddTypeExtensions<T extends MIObject>
    The interface IMdfWriteListAddTypeExtensions defines some method extensions for MDF child lists to create and add new MDF object instances.
    IMdfWriteListExtensions<O extends MIObject,R extends com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.commoncore.autosar.MIReferrable,D extends com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIHasDefinition>
    The IMdfWriteListExtensions provides extension methods for MDF model child lists.
    IMdfWriteSingleConfigurator<T extends MIObject>
    * The IMdfWriteSingleConfigurator provides means to configure the write navigator access (see IMdfModelNavigator for a single MDF object.
    IModelReadApiEntryPoint
    IModelReadApiEntryPoint is the entry point for MDF model read access.
    IOperations
    IOperations is the entry point for some complex operations on the AUTOSAR data model.
    ITransactionApi
    The ITransactionApi provides some transaction specific means which are available inside a running transaction only.
    ITransactionApiEntryPoint
    ITransactionApiEntryPoint is the entry point for MDF model write access and model transaction handling.
    ITransactionHistoryApi
    ITransactionHistoryApi is the entry point for dealing with the transaction history.
    IVarianceApi
    The IVarianceApi provides some means to deal with model variance.
    IVarianceApiEntryPoint
    IVarianceApiEntryPoint is the entry point for handling variant model content.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EModelNavigatorCreationMode

    EModelNavigatorCreationMode

    The EModelNavigatorCreationMode enum defines how the model navigator shall create model content in the write mode.
